---

<Layout title={`Speaking - ${config.title}`} description="Keynote speaker and technology thought leader on AI, cloud computing, and digital transformation">
	<section class="speaking-header">
		<h1>Speaking & Media</h1>
		<p class="subtitle">Sharing insights on AI, cloud computing, and digital transformation</p>
	</section>

	<section class="speaking-intro">
		<p>With over 30 years of experience at the forefront of technology innovation, I bring unique perspectives on AI transformation, multi-agent systems, cloud computing, and cybersecurity. From testifying before Congress to advising at the White House, I've had the privilege of shaping technology policy and strategy at the highest levels.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="speaking-hero">
		<a href={speakingImage.src} target="_blank">
			<Image 
				src={speakingImage} 
				alt="John Engates speaking at GigaOM Conference" 
				class="speaking-photo clickable"
				width={600}
				height={400}
				format="webp"
				quality={90}
			/>
		</a>
		<p class="photo-caption">Speaking at GigaOM Structure 2013 on cloud infrastructure and digital transformation</p>
		<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W5M8yt5gCw0&list=PLCLrzcAZ57SXu-5Gv03Zo4X7YtnQLmri5&index=7" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="interview-link">Watch Interview →</a>
	</section>

	<section class="featured-appearances">
